Library to handle Moment Tensor Potential through the Stochastic Self Consistent harmonic approximation
The scripts folder contains the scripts to execute the code.
SSCHA.py         contains the main workflow for the SSCHA + MLIP automated protocol
potential.mtp    represents an example of Moment Tensor potential of level 10
utils.py         contains the input scripts for the first principle calculations and the cluster handling.

To run the program correctly, place the SSCHA.py, the potential.mtp, the Pseudo folder and the utils file in a single folder.
